snippet.title: Stagehands! Reveal Trailer (PC, Nintendo Switch)
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: http://bit.ly/SHsteam


Let’s get the show on the road! 



Set up the stage with your friends and face pure chaos in this 2-4 player co-op, guaranteed to make you break a leg. As a team, prepare to improvise in the face of sabotage and environmental mayhem. The fate of the play is in your paws! 



Stagehands! is coming to PC and Switch in 2021.



Learn more & subscribe to our newsletter: http://playstagehands.com


Follow us on Twitter: http://twitter.com/playstagehands
Follow us on Facebook: http://facebook.com/playstagehands
